title: Are You a Victim?
itunes:title: Are You a Victim?
description:
Episode 528 - If we are not careful, we can fall into the trap of playing the victim. This is one of the worst spots to be in the world because then we are not in control of our lives. In this episode, I dive into this topic and teach you how to be in control of our lives so that we can change it.
